            <thetext>Every store creates internally a request to fetch the data. In some cases, it is necessary to change some settings on the request to fit it the needs of the developer. Therefore, we should provide a way of configuring the created request.
A good idea could be the offering of another method in the store delegate, which can configure the created request given as a parameter. This would be equal to configuring a list item in the list controller of the data binding.</thetext>
